            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Janedlj/" class=" " title="海狸君">海狸君</a>
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="22755910">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">“人是美的核心和主体。”。而“人”之主在是“生命之真”，人欲达“真”唯在“自由”。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-11-26 21:55</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">3人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>“人是美的核心和主体。”。而“人”之主在是“生命之真”，人欲达“真”唯在“自由”。</q></blockquote>
