            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="32787072">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">粗糙刚硬的现实，打磨掉我一层柔嫩的皮肤，打磨掉我许多纤细精致的感觉的触须，把我也变成了粗糙与刚硬。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2014-09-07 13:33</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">1人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                粗糙刚硬的现实，打磨掉我一层柔嫩的皮肤，打磨掉我许多纤细精致的感觉的触须，把我也变成了粗糙与刚硬。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
